name: Boquet-manager
tagline: Useful Java FX application for managing XML files which are consist of sattelite channels information (Dbox2 Neutrino, CST Trinity Sat NeutrinoHD )
body:
### Welcome on my page of developing Boquet-manger.
It's Java FX desktop application to provide easy way for managing sat channels.
Nice Java FX UI, which i hope will give a user nice experience.

### Authors and Contributors
Currently me (Alexander Orlovsky) i am only one person who works on this project full time, if you wish to contact me here is email: javaprofi [at]gmx.de
